Preferences and Final Good Technology
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection*

\series medium
There is a continuum of individuals indexed by 
\begin_inset Formula $i\in[0,1]$
\end_inset

.
 Each individual maximizes
\begin_inset Foot
