\begin_inset Formula $q_{j}$
\end_inset

, enters the final good production function.
 Look into this eventually, it doesn't seem like an important detail.
 In both cases the growth rate of the economy is just the growth rate of
 
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{q}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\end_inset

 
\end_layout

